Zeitgeist plugin for Totem
**************************

To use this plugin:

* Install Zeitgeist 0.3 (or greater) so that the python library is available system-wide.
* Run the install.sh script which will copy the plugin to '~/.local/share/totem/plugins'.
* Launch Totem, choose Edit -> Plugins, and select the Zeitgeist plugin.

To update plugin changes:
* Run the install.sh script to recopy the plugin files.

